00:38:48,300 --> 00:38:49,390
How you doing?

467
00:38:54,100 --> 00:38:56,690
it's just so unfair.

468
00:38:57,700 --> 00:39:00,890
I mean, she's never gonna be able to read
any of the articles I've written,

469
00:39:01,200 --> 00:39:02,790
you know, or meet jimmy.

470
00:39:10,400 --> 00:39:12,890
She's never gonna get to know
the person that I've become.

471
00:39:15,100 --> 00:39:16,690
It's a good thing I told her.

472
00:39:19,100 --> 00:39:20,190
You did?

